              A personal AI that remembers you, lives in your messaging apps, and actually does things ‚Äî email, calendar, research, reminders. Set up in 5 minutes.
            </p>
            <form id="hero-form" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md">
              <input
                type="email"
                placeholder="Enter your email"
                required
                class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg text-text-primary placeholder:text-text-muted focus:outline-none focus:border-blue focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue transition-colors"
              />
