        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-blue/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all reveal">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üß†</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-heading mb-3">No Memory</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">ChatGPT forgets you every conversation. Your AI should know your preferences, your schedule, your life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-blue/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all reveal">
