          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-blue/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all reveal">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üîí</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold font-heading mb-3">No Autonomy</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">They wait for you to open an app. A real assistant works in the background, 24/7.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto reveal">
          The DIY alternative? A server, Docker, API keys, DNS, and ongoing maintenance. <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">95% of people who want a persistent AI assistant can't set one up.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== 4. THE SOLUTION ========== -->
    <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-surface/30">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold font-heading mb-4">Personal AI, Zero Setup</h2>
