            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">Email, calendar, web search, reminders, research.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-2xl p-7 hover:border-blue/50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all reveal">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üß†</div>
